{"tid":184490,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【好方便！】匯豐推流動編碼及指紋認證功能","createTime":"2017-04-03T00:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T12:18:52.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15efe1137dce7ab88d0615fdceef3328928af20f","tid":184490,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20170330/s00010/2d24f8f2ad1778c32363ad975a642b36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20170330%2Fs00010%2F2d24f8f2ad1778c32363ad975a642b36.jpg&h=b113cd65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20170330/s00010/2a692d20fc7085fcd6a3f4c5b7eeeaff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20170330%2Fs00010%2F2a692d20fc7085fcd6a3f4c5b7eeeaff.jpg&h=1e895f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n匯豐香港推出流動保安編碼及指紋認證功能。鍾林枝攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20170330/s00010/2a6e552ad996875d07dba0b4aeda7886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20170330%2Fs00010%2F2a6e552ad996875d07dba0b4aeda7886.jpg&h=b14ea02f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n匯豐香港區零售銀行及財富管理業務電子服務平台主管(左)艾俊安/匯豐香港區零售銀行及財富管理業務電子服務平台高級經理(右)張瑞欣。鍾林枝攝<br />\n<br />\n匯豐宣布，將於四月初推出流動保安編碼及指紋認證功能，所有個人網上理財客戶可更方便快捷地使用流動及網上理財，至於已啟用流動保安編碼的客戶，日後亦毋須再使用實體保安編碼器。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐香港區零售銀行及財富管理業務主管欣格雷表示，此項新功能讓流動理財客戶用指尖一按，即可完成登入驗證，冀可推動更多客戶轉用流動設備進行交易，該行未來將繼續開拓並提升數碼銀行服務的渠道。<br />\n<br />\n全新的流動保安編碼取代原有實體保安編碼器，內置在智能手機內；已啟動流動的保安編碼的客戶可使用全面的電子理財服務，毋須再額外攜帶保安編碼器。<br />\n<br />\n另外，匯豐為Apple裝置用戶提供便利的指紋認證功能，讓流動理財用戶可使用指紋登入匯豐理財應用程式；至於Android裝置亦即將推出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1490854375037&amp;issue=20170330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1490854375037%26issue%3D20170330&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=361e7938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1490854375037&amp;issue=20170330</a>"},{"pid":"7b4541d1918e9400c2a0d297ca52c624c0ce1a85","tid":184490,"uid":11549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:02:42.000Z","msg":"IT狗用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a958946b07a71ef2a53069d087a8851d82e05d","tid":184490,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:03:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe9526d2c41ab154ccc6dd05b86b5074fe969d94","tid":184490,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:04:29.000Z","msg":"岩岩被炒既it狗既產物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8270b9327e7e03024a4467e077d98d666dce999b","tid":184490,"uid":19703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:20:57.000Z","msg":"依家先整touch id login<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42e95a8d1124db436c3bad09624469f142c92d9","tid":184490,"uid":96565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家先整touch id login<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常<br />\n係獅子銀行搞新野即係搏炒"},{"pid":"75e4c03a65b1dd6cbd3ad28fb3d47197074a7190","tid":184490,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"Citi一早就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5595b50e583652313aab307cd655de57b3f0cbf4","tid":184490,"uid":27609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾，而家先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵你連續6年業續倒退返5x$ 啦廢柴"},{"pid":"ccb6887b8a880db72f943be07ab509e5a280258e","tid":184490,"uid":44512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:29:15.000Z","msg":"其實寶體既用意唔係驚避免電子產品比人Hack 左而多重保障咩，依家又電子化番 同當初apps 個密碼有咩分別<img src=\"